{"tid":806654,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到連登原來真係紅底","createTime":"2018-09-05T00:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T12:51:06.000Z","uid":89394,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3031be669774193e471a8a4e1db73e736cd1e46","tid":806654,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"琴日開完個post走咗去訓<br />\n訓訓下就望到個post入面勁俾人屌<br />\n屌到好大壓力好唔開心<br />\n想成個連登戶口delete咗佢連埋啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後本身諗住fb pm admin del account<br />\n但好似無人應咁<br />\n於是就踩上連登個總部叫佢del account<br />\n<br />\n上到去個office勁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開門俾我個人係講野唔正嘅呀嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為自己搞錯地方<br />\n之後有個又係講唔正嘅呀叔嚟問我係咪del account<br />\n我話係，佢就帶咗我去入啲一間房<br />\n之後發現全部都係大陸狗嘅同事<br />\n個講唔正野嘅呀叔叫我入返ac資料就可以del ac<br />\n屌，我睇到咁撚樣梗係即刻怒填del ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我就醒咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7848a754f264a6b0261bedf43af399b734110fc","tid":806654,"uid":87741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 零分重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cf395881ba6ebfd5041f0355d16fe66280ebff","tid":806654,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7848a754f264a6b0261bedf43af399b734110fc","tid":806654,"uid":87741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 零分重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:00:43.000Z","msg":"打漏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb8b80dba6fa567358c9a8691f65d5e4e37b6f7","tid":806654,"uid":105908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"都好 起碼你訓到 冇再喊"},{"pid":